'''Asegbar''' (deg unti tasegbart), d anaẓur amsadur i yettbuddun ṣṣifa n tfekka-s akk neɣ taɣect-is kan i kra n uwadem deg tmezgunt, deg usaru, deg tiliẓri neɣ di rrady. Meḥsub yettidir kra n uneḍru d yiḥulfan deg teswiɛt-nni akken i ten-id-yefka weḍris neɣ taqsiṭ i yekkat ad d-yesken i imferrjen.
